high_descs: walk to the sofa where the open box is.
Pick up the knife from the ottoman.
Take the knife to the sidetable.
Put the knife away in the sidetable.
walk over to the coffeetable.

take that knife to the sidetable.

high_descs: Turn right to the end of the room and turn left to reach the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the ottoman.
Turn left to reach the sidetable.
Put the knife behind the apple on the sidetable.
Turn around to reach the coffeetable across the room.
Pick up the knife from the dresser.
Turn left to reach the sidetable across the room.
Put the knife next to the other knife on the sidetable.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight towards the wall, then left to the blue seat in front of the table, standing in between the wall and the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the seat.
Turn left and go towards the sidetable ahead.
Place the knife on top of the sidetable next to the apple.
Go back towards the area with the blue seat and go to the coffeetable next to it.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Return to the sidetable you placed the first knife on.
Place the second knife down next to the first on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two knives on top of a SideTable.
